and weapons transform you into a damage dealing machine.<br><br>No matter what anyone says I love my Ragebringer. I consider myself very lucky at obtaining it at level 50 and in a weeks time of questing for it. I have met only 2 rogues on my server who has actually banked their epics because of upgrades from NTOV. <br><br>Bottom when I made my rogue he did not come equiped with a Ragebringer. I worked my @$$ to get my epic and I'm enjoying the hell out of it.<br><br>MM ~<br> <p><html><FONT SIZE=2><font color="#1E90FF"><center><b><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=79937>Misda Meanor</a><br> Halas Finest  Shadow Dweller</b><br><i><FONT SIZE=1>"Expect my visit when the darkness comes. The night I think is best for hiding all"</i> </a> <font color="#1E90FF"><center><FONT SIZE=2><br><br><b>Khama Mustafa  <br>Retired Warlord of Grobb </b><a></font></html>                                                                                              </p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uprenn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Prenn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/6/02 3:52:08 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseranthallgripeswishes.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4517.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Grats on your Freebringer!!</span><hr size=1> How can you have typed that post, and still not understand what he said? <p><center><font size=2><font color=ashen><a href=http://www.geocities.com/pren_tribunal/pren.txt><u>Pren, Human Master</u></a> on The Tribunal Server<br></font></font><font size=1>We came to drop bombs<br>Callin' every man in the arms<br>And yo, sound to your law<br><I>Smartbomb</i><font><br><img src=http://home.mindspring