pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseranthallgripeswishes.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4517.topic&index=13>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Grats on your Freebringer!!</span><hr size=1> Third isle? You can do third isle sky with one group.<br><br>Try seventh isle.<br><br><br><br><br>Monk epic isn't one of the most difficult epics. The epic fights are doable in one day. The karnor pipe and raster are the difficult parts, and the brothers of the lost circle no longer drop the robe 100% (they should have never dropped it to begin with.)<br><br>However, you can't do the monk epic 11 freaking times in a couple of hours like people do the general.<br><br><br>As for difficult? Yes, other than monk epic (Which has worse haste than rogue epic if you're in a group with an enchanter. Free 40% item haste is not to be overlooked) you have to kill considerably more powerful mobs.<br><br>Then druid epic. Faydedar isn't too bad. Offhand ranger epic is simple as well, but the whole jade reaver thing makes it a bitch.<br><br>Shaman epic is the next easiest, and it requires an uncommon spawn in fear triggered by a miniboss.<br><br>Wizard epic is decently easy as well.<br><br><br><br><br><br><br>Mage epic requires you kill that super dude in CoM with the insane ae.<br><br>Warrior epic requires Severilious/Hoshkar (most difficult mob pre velious who still is extremely badass), queen in chardok, spiroc lord in air...<br><br>Cleric epic requires chardok king and ixiblat ferr.<br><br>Enchanter epic requires a rare spawn in fear, a rare drop in hate, and one camp WORSE than ragefire. A guild enchanter camped the neriak part over 4 days straight before it popped.<br><br>Primary ranger epic requires a drop off innoruuk/rare drop off the minibosses.<br><br>Let's not talk about the white scale bard epic thing. There are a LOT of people who are too high to kill vox but aren't high enough to kill gore, or simply lose the spawn race.<br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br>But my point was, this guy made a post saying it took him 5 months to get his warrior epic. Then he got his twink rogue one in a week. And he can't understand why a warrior friend of his called it a freebringer?<br><br>The exact reason of how easy it is to get, and how long you will wield it, and how hard it is for most people to get 40% haste, all combined is why it's called freebringer.<br><br>It's obviously the best melee epic, hands down. Not knocking it as a weapon, because it certainly kicks ass.<br><br><br>(BTW, monk epic effect overwrites strength of nature and firefist/grim aura. When you have 40% or better spell haste from an enchanter or shaman, the monk epic effect is worse than the rogue. This isn't a complaint, simple truth.) <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uandurian.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Andurian</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/6/02 3:06:40 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseranthallgripeswishes.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4517.topic&index=14>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://andurian.homestead.com/files/Spike01.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Grats on your Freebringer!!</span><hr size=1> While I'm very proud of my Rb.<br>It is a easy quest, after loosing my first box from a cabin repop behind me :/ . I went through and completed the quest to renux in 2 days. Naked hate run and all.<br><br>Then I spend 2 months killing phinny 7 times, and watching the cabin in Kith for my robe.<br><br>All and all, my Burning Rapier took longer for me to get. Actually a bit more proud of the BR becuase I know very few get it anymore. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span 